[{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-0783","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-0783.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-0526","title":"X.Org X11 服务器未授权访问漏洞","description":"tags.<value>X Window System（X11）服务器存在访问控制配置不当漏洞。当管理员执行 \"xhost +\" 命令或类似操作禁用 X 服务器的访问控制机制后，未经身份认证的远程攻击者可直接连接至目标系统的 X 服务，进而查看屏幕内容、记录键盘输入、执行任意命令，完全控制用户桌面会话。该漏洞影响配置有 X11 服务的 Unix/Linux 工作站和服务器，攻击者无需凭据即可在图形界面下实施窃密与破坏操作。修复方案为启用 X 服务器的访问控制列表（ACL），通过 \"xhost -\" 恢复默认限制或使用 SSH 隧道加密 X11 转发。","severity":"CRITICAL","score":10.0,"aliases":["CVE-1999-0526"],"sources":["epss"],"published":"1997-07-01T04:00:00.000","updated":"2026-06-16T21:48:35.033","remediation":"立即在 X server 所在主机执行 `xhost -` 或 `xhost -+` 撤销 `xhost +` 造成的全局开放访问控制，改用 `~/.Xauthority` 中的 MIT-MAGIC-COOKIE 密钥进行认证，对远程显示场景使用 `ssh -X` 或 `ssh -Y` 建立加密隧道并在允许列表中仅保留 `127.0.0.1`，同时执行 `chmod 600 ~/.Xauthority` 收紧密钥文件权限，杜绝无参数的 `xhost +`。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-16T00:00:00Z","references":["http://www.kb.cert.org/vuls/id/704969","https://github.com/trickest/cve/blob/6e5939e8074723d33adaf5b2f8b0352edab9ba8d/1999/CVE-1999-0526.md","https://github.com/CVEProject/cvelistV5/blob/37cec437f4ca5dbafb8ef4c4921c71da1b289b8f/cves/1999/0xxx/CVE-1999-0526.json","https://github.com/BrianWGray/cmty-nexpose-checks/blob/13b1c2f4cca654217a136c8eec10f7f6e18f35b8/cmty-x11-cve-1999-0526.vck","https://github.com/lvbibir/lvbibir.github.io/blob/563f70566900245eb0ea2d9afc1f1d378e9a0ed5/content/posts/tech/cve-1999-0526.md","https://github.com/LiuCan01/cve-list-pro/blob/78b55511cee3604c22d518e32822f0435d0cacc0/cve-list/CVE-1999/CVE-1999-0526","https://github.com/demisto/content/blob/f0f3f1996ab0ab86cf0719cf8b65d7b5741a97bb/Packs/GreyNoise/.secrets-ignore","https://github.com/e-m-b-a/emba/blob/968abdc74763b43a3cdd216fbb1950cab484f982/config/msf_cve-db.txt","https://github.com/Patrowl/PatrowlHearsData/blob/f581b54f28a314b57ac171b83d3b2d21db7414a0/CVE/data/1999/CVE-1999-0526.json","https://github.com/MrWQ/vulnerability-paper/blob/fcbdb421b62aef6ccac59a1887d94687f4faf9d6/bugs/%E7%AB%AF%E5%8F%A3%E6%BC%8F%E6%B4%9E%E5%85%A8%E9%9B%86.md","https://github.com/github/advisory-database/blob/11845a9fe6e6b4d82150d9fd8a4257b88a244a45/advisories/unreviewed/2022/04/GHSA-fv34-2r8h-94mm/GHSA-fv34-2r8h-94mm.json"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-0783.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-0435","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-0435.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-0250","title":"Dan Bernstein Qmail SMTP 命令处理拒绝服务漏洞","description":"Qmail 1.01 的 SMTP 组件在处理超长命令时存在拒绝服务漏洞。远程攻击者无需认证即可向目标服务器的 25 端口发送特制长 SMTP 命令，导致 qmail-smtpd 进程崩溃或异常终止，从而中断邮件服务。该漏洞影响 Dan Bernstein Qmail 1.01 版本，攻击复杂度低，且无需任何权限，可被用于阻断正常邮件收发功能。","severity":"CRITICAL","score":10.0,"aliases":["CVE-1999-0250"],"sources":["epss"],"published":"1997-07-01T04:00:00.000","updated":"2026-06-16T21:48:00.120","remediation":"立即升级至 Qmail 1.03 或更高版本，或在编译时添加 qmail-smtpd.c 中对输入行长度（LINE_MAX）的显式检查。如不便升级，可在 SMTP 服务前端部署流量过滤规则，限制单行 SMTP 命令长度不超过 512 字节。长期建议迁移至 Netqmail 补丁集（netqmail 1.06）以获得持续维护。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-14T00:00:00Z","references":["http://cr.yp.to/qmail/venema.html","http://marc.info/?l=bugtraq&m=87602558319024&w=2","http://www.ornl.gov/its/archives/mailing-lists/qmail/1997/06/threads.html","https://github.com/trickest/cve/blob/34851454a7b07498072de47d56f63daa4a4f524d/1999/CVE-1999-0250.md","https://github.com/CVEProject/cvelistV5/blob/ab6ab436962e16237b21ed9d4458dafc38c692fc/cves/1999/0xxx/CVE-1999-0250.json","https://github.com/LiuCan01/cve-list-pro/blob/78b55511cee3604c22d518e32822f0435d0cacc0/cve-list/CVE-1999/CVE-1999-0250","https://github.com/edoardottt/missing-cve-nuclei-templates/blob/36c16d53eb6071e39cfc3cf88e99f1b340ec913b/data/year/1999.txt","https://github.com/aquasecurity/vuln-list-redhat/blob/601a95d57be2a57306cd88389c2251f34b2fbcc1/csaf-vex/1999/cve-1999-0250.json","https://github.com/Patrowl/PatrowlHearsData/blob/a55bddfc5dd568e972e08b703ab596ed3580b7ba/CVE/data/1999/CVE-1999-0250.json","https://github.com/github/advisory-database/blob/49899a53e9c2e620c99e0234afe3c50e512ad851/advisories/unreviewed/2022/04/GHSA-wq5m-pq24-j5cv/GHSA-wq5m-pq24-j5cv.json","https://github.com/feng-li/tools-for-data-science-course/blob/8e62d47ee8ffbebe9a0e50aee193617f83883118/2019spring/2017312271/result.txt","https://github.com/SpeeDr00t/speedr00t.github.com/blob/0380f0c2190556fabe90257cb6c0034a42f68951/securityfocus/0x83000/82079/info.html","https://github.com/nomi-sec/NVD-Database/blob/23dc120c34402aaa65883c51c1d03b3cb02c20cb/1999/CVE-1999-0250.json"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-0435.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-0407","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-0407.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-0219","title":"Cat Soft Serv-U FTP Server 远程缓冲区溢出漏洞","description":"Cat Soft Serv-U FTP Server 2.5 存在远程缓冲区溢出漏洞。已认证的远程攻击者可通过向 FTP 服务发送超长的 CWD（切换目录）或 LS（列出文件）命令触发缓冲区溢出，导致服务进程崩溃，造成拒绝服务。该漏洞影响 Serv-U FTP Server 2.5 版本，攻击者只需拥有有效账号即可利用，无需其他特殊权限。","severity":"HIGH","score":7.8,"aliases":["CVE-1999-0219"],"sources":["exploitdb"],"published":"1997-07-01T04:00:00.000","updated":"2026-06-16T21:47:56.290","remediation":"升级至 Serv-U 2.5a 或更高版本可修复此缓冲区溢出漏洞。当前最新版为 SolarWinds Serv-U 15.x，建议立即升级并开启自动更新。如无法升级，可在防火墙限制 FTP 端口（21/TCP）仅对可信来源开放，并禁用匿名用户写权限作为临时缓解。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-16T00:00:00Z","references":["http://marc.info/?l=ntbugtraq&m=92574916930144&w=2","http://marc.info/?l=ntbugtraq&m=92582581330282&w=2","http://www.securityfocus.com/bid/269","https://exchange.xforce.ibmcloud.com/vulnerabilities/205","https://www.exploit-db.com/exploits/19218","https://github.com/CVEProject/cvelistV5/blob/ead50dc12e50bdd7f50b53d9d01c9f9946862c44/cves/1999/0xxx/CVE-1999-0219.json","https://github.com/LiuCan01/cve-list-pro/blob/78b55511cee3604c22d518e32822f0435d0cacc0/cve-list/CVE-1999/CVE-1999-0219","https://github.com/yarencheng/cve-devops-playground/blob/45be3b4afd9c4397ee32a5cbf6819a590220b0c1/content/CVE-1999-0219.md","https://github.com/Patrowl/PatrowlHearsData/blob/4ed191c1149de50e461e9a357f4a3a22e603f0d1/CVE/data/1999/CVE-1999-0219.json","https://github.com/github/advisory-database/blob/b7a93df7f7051799495805bc211adea8d202dae7/advisories/unreviewed/2022/04/GHSA-5495-52g6-8q95/GHSA-5495-52g6-8q95.json","https://github.com/feng-li/tools-for-data-science-course/blob/8e62d47ee8ffbebe9a0e50aee193617f83883118/2019spring/2017312271/result.txt","https://github.com/blackhook/nessus-plugins/blob/64177d96abbb07c58cf7e131046b067ebc61fcb5/F/ftp_servu_dos.nasl","https://github.com/nomi-sec/NVD-Database/blob/23dc120c34402aaa65883c51c1d03b3cb02c20cb/1999/CVE-1999-0219.json","https://github.com/jdkoftinoff/mb-linux-msli/blob/8adb103e34af9ff1d8d122e9ee2a1808836f0a14/uClinux-dist/user/nessus/nessus-plugins/scripts/ftp_overflow.nasl","https://github.com/KTZgraph/sarenka/blob/f1fb931ab722d6c096d581ed6e3c5966d799fbaa/sarenka/feeds/cve_details/cve_all_details_154400_154500.json"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-0407.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-0377","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-0377.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-0195","title":"Sun RPC Portmapper 源IP地址欺骗拒绝服务漏洞","description":"Linux Kernel 2.6.20.1 中的 RPC Portmapper 组件存在源 IP 地址验证缺陷，远程攻击者可通过伪造 127.0.0.1 等源 IP 地址向目标系统发送特制的 RPC 请求，实现注册/注销 RPC 服务或伪装合法 RPC 服务，导致目标系统拒绝服务。该漏洞影响 Linux Kernel 2.6.20.1 版本，CVSS 评分 5.0，危害等级中危。","severity":"MEDIUM","score":5.0,"aliases":["CVE-1999-0195"],"sources":["epss"],"published":"1997-07-01T04:00:00.000","updated":"2026-06-16T21:47:53.223","remediation":"升级 Linux 内核至 2.6.20.1 以上版本，该漏洞已在后续版本修复。使用 iptables 限制对 TCP/UDP 111 端口的访问来源，仅允许可信 IP 段连接 RPC portmapper。如不需要 RPC 服务，建议在 `/etc/init.d/` 中停止 portmap/rpcbind 服务并通过 `chkconfig portmap off` 禁止开机自启。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-13T00:00:00Z","references":["https://www.cve.org/CVERecord?id=CVE-1999-0195"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-0377.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-0367","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-0367.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-0184","title":"ISC BIND 动态DNS更新不当漏洞","description":"BIND DNS 服务器在编译时启用 -DALLOW_UPDATES 选项后，会允许未经验证的动态 DNS 更新请求。远程攻击者可利用该功能向目标服务器发送恶意动态更新数据包，从而篡改或添加 DNS 记录，导致域名解析劫持、流量重定向等严重后果。该漏洞影响多种 Unix/Linux 系统上运行的 BIND 服务，CVSS 评分 6.4，危害等级中危。","severity":"MEDIUM","score":6.4,"aliases":["CVE-1999-0184"],"sources":["epss"],"published":"1997-07-01T04:00:00.000","updated":"2026-06-16T21:47:46.770","remediation":"重新编译 BIND 时移除 -DALLOW_UPDATES 编译选项以禁用动态更新功能；如业务需要动态 DNS 更新，请在 named.conf 中使用 allow-update ACL 限定仅允许信任网段（如 10.0.0.0/8）发起更新请求，并配置 TSIG 密钥签名认证确保更新来源合法性；同时升级至 BIND 9.x 或更高版本以获取完整的访问控制和身份验证机制。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-13T00:00:00Z","references":["https://exchange.xforce.ibmcloud.com/vulnerabilities/CVE-1999-0184"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-0367.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-0318","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-0318.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-0153","title":"Microsoft Windows 3.11/95/NT NetBIOS 带外数据拒绝服务漏洞（WinNuke）","description":"Windows 95/NT 系统的 NetBIOS 协议实现存在缺陷，远程攻击者可通过向目标系统的 139 端口发送特制的 OOB（Out of Band）带外数据包，触发系统内存访问异常，导致目标系统蓝屏崩溃（BSOD），造成拒绝服务。该漏洞影响 Windows 3.11/95/NT 3.5.1/NT 4.0 等早期版本，攻击无需认证，利用门槛极低。","severity":"MEDIUM","score":5.0,"aliases":["CVE-1999-0153"],"sources":["exploitdb"],"published":"1997-07-01T04:00:00.000","updated":"2026-06-16T21:47:42.847","remediation":"升级到 Windows 2000 及以上版本（WinNuke 攻击已在后续版本中修复）。若无法升级，在防火墙或路由器上阻止外部对 TCP 端口 139（NetBIOS Session Service）和 137（NetBIOS Name Service）的入站访问；在网络属性中解除「Microsoft 网络的文件和打印机共享」绑定以关闭 NetBIOS over TCP/IP。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-14T00:00:00Z","references":["http://www.osvdb.org/1666","https://www.exploit-db.com/exploits/20440","https://github.com/CVEProject/cvelistV5/blob/269e5b2b6ea60fdb4a03411be38d3e381b26e4c4/cves/1999/0xxx/CVE-1999-0153.json","https://github.com/LiuCan01/cve-list-pro/blob/78b55511cee3604c22d518e32822f0435d0cacc0/cve-list/CVE-1999/CVE-1999-0153","https://github.com/aquasecurity/vuln-list-redhat/blob/601a95d57be2a57306cd88389c2251f34b2fbcc1/csaf-vex/1999/cve-1999-0153.json","https://github.com/yarencheng/cve-devops-playground/blob/9074597bd191efd66c2a6bf1f5d8e60bc4801a90/content/CVE-1999-0153.md","https://github.com/Patrowl/PatrowlHearsData/blob/2f876a2c24d5ccd5bbd081f09e801e580536456a/CVE/data/1999/CVE-1999-0153.json","https://github.com/github/advisory-database/blob/49899a53e9c2e620c99e0234afe3c50e512ad851/advisories/unreviewed/2022/04/GHSA-g9jq-2w39-657g/GHSA-g9jq-2w39-657g.json","https://github.com/rhuitl/uClinux/blob/0486e80a025dccbe4a2213715a2ab8a5063ea86b/user/snort/drop-rules/sid-msg.map","https://github.com/feng-li/tools-for-data-science-course/blob/8e62d47ee8ffbebe9a0e50aee193617f83883118/2019spring/2017312271/result.txt","https://github.com/blackhook/nessus-plugins/blob/64177d96abbb07c58cf7e131046b067ebc61fcb5/W/winnuke.nasl","https://github.com/slacker247/GPDA/blob/fa9006d0877a691f1ddffe88799c844a3e8a669a/Sodi/Run/IDSrules/rule.194"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-0318.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-0310","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-0310.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-0150","title":"Perl fingerd 远程命令执行漏洞","description":"Perl 实现的 fingerd 程序存在远程命令执行漏洞。由于 fingerd 在处理远程用户输入的查询参数时未经过滤直接传递给系统命令执行，未经身份认证的远程攻击者可通过向目标主机的 finger 服务（tcp/79）发送特制请求，在目标系统上以 fingerd 运行权限执行任意命令，从而完全控制受影响主机。该漏洞影响多个 Unix 系统上使用 Perl 实现的 fingerd 程序，无需认证即可远程利用，危害严重。","severity":"HIGH","score":7.5,"aliases":["CVE-1999-0150"],"sources":["epss"],"published":"1997-07-01T04:00:00.000","updated":"2026-06-16T21:47:42.367","remediation":"立即停用并移除 finger 服务（该协议已过时），或升级到不受影响的版本。如必须运行 finger 服务，务必对用户输入进行严格的 shell 元字符过滤，避免将输入直接传递给 `system()`、`exec()`、反引号等命令执行函数；同时在防火墙层面阻止外部对 79/TCP 端口的访问作为临时缓解。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-13T00:00:00Z","references":["https://exchange.xforce.ibmcloud.com/vulnerabilities/CVE-1999-0150"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-0310.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-0301","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-0301.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-0147","title":"Glimpse GlimpseHTTP/WebGlimpse aglimpse CGI 远程命令执行漏洞","description":"GlimpseHTTP 1.0/2.0 及 WebGlimpse 1.0 的 aglimpse CGI 组件中存在远程命令执行漏洞。攻击者可通过向该 CGI 程序发送特制的管道命令参数，利用服务器端对用户输入过滤不严的缺陷，在目标系统上以 Web 服务器进程权限执行任意命令。该漏洞影响早期 GlimpseHTTP 及 WebGlimpse 版本，CVSS 评分 7.5，危害等级高，无需认证即可远程触发。","severity":"HIGH","score":7.5,"aliases":["CVE-1999-0147"],"sources":["exploitdb"],"published":"1997-07-01T04:00:00.000","updated":"2026-06-16T21:47:41.957","remediation":"立即停止使用 GlimpseHTTP/WebGlimpse，从 cgi-bin 目录中移除 aglimpse 可执行文件，并迁移至现代受支持的 Web 服务器（如 Apache/Nginx）。如无法立即迁移，可在 Web 服务器层面限制 aglimpse 脚本执行权限，设置仅授权 IP 可访问 cgi-bin 目录，同时移除不必要的 CGI 程序以减少攻击面。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-14T00:00:00Z","references":["https://exchange.xforce.ibmcloud.com/vulnerabilities/CVE-1999-0147","https://www.exploit-db.com/exploits/20449","https://github.com/CVEProject/cvelistV5/blob/ab669d9fb37e52ed0619cb2b8265d34528fbe875/cves/1999/0xxx/CVE-1999-0147.json","https://github.com/LiuCan01/cve-list-pro/blob/78b55511cee3604c22d518e32822f0435d0cacc0/cve-list/CVE-1999/CVE-1999-0147","https://github.com/aquasecurity/vuln-list-redhat/blob/601a95d57be2a57306cd88389c2251f34b2fbcc1/csaf-vex/1999/cve-1999-0147.json","https://github.com/yarencheng/cve-devops-playground/blob/9074597bd191efd66c2a6bf1f5d8e60bc4801a90/content/CVE-1999-0147.md","https://github.com/Patrowl/PatrowlHearsData/blob/2ed73314b4d66512efbb22e0644e615bc00001f2/CVE/data/1999/CVE-1999-0147.json","https://github.com/github/advisory-database/blob/49899a53e9c2e620c99e0234afe3c50e512ad851/advisories/unreviewed/2022/04/GHSA-j92f-fc3c-68gj/GHSA-j92f-fc3c-68gj.json","https://github.com/rhuitl/uClinux/blob/0486e80a025dccbe4a2213715a2ab8a5063ea86b/user/snort/drop-rules/sid-msg.map","https://github.com/blackhook/nessus-plugins/blob/64177d96abbb07c58cf7e131046b067ebc61fcb5/G/glimpse.nasl","https://github.com/olbat/nvdcve/blob/d21eb36f6164170df89822577def7df5351966d2/nvdcve/CVE-1999-0147.json","https://github.com/intSpLoiT/intframework/blob/eabaa799d0260aa52b735fa9769266d1ce4b64ef/modules/cve_list.txt"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":["https://raw.githubusercontent.com/adysec/AVE/main/pocs/1999/POC-AVE-1999-0301.toml"],"repo_exp_urls":["https://raw.githubusercontent.com/adysec/AVE/main/exploits/1999/EXP-AVE-1999-0301.toml"],"has_poc":true,"has_exp":true,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-0301.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-0252","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-0252.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-0111","title":"IBM AIX RIP v1 路由欺骗漏洞","description":"RIP v1 是一种距离向量路由协议，其设计缺陷在于未对路由更新报文进行身份认证，导致攻击者可通过伪造 RIP 广播报文向目标系统注入虚假路由条目。AIX 系统上运行的 RIP v1 服务存在欺骗漏洞，远程未认证攻击者可在同一广播域内发送精心构造的 RIP 响应报文，篡改目标主机的路由表，将流量重定向至攻击者控制的恶意节点，进而实现中间人攻击、信息窃取或拒绝服务。该漏洞影响 AIX 系统上启用了 RIP v1 服务的配置，CVSS 评分 5.0，危害等级中危。","severity":"MEDIUM","score":5.0,"aliases":["CVE-1999-0111"],"sources":["epss"],"published":"1997-07-01T04:00:00.000","updated":"2026-06-16T21:47:36.543","remediation":"建议升级支持 RIPv2 的路由软件以启用 MD5 认证，或迁移至 OSPF 等认证型路由协议；在边界路由器上配置被动接口并实施 RIP 路由过滤（distribute-list），仅允许与已知邻居通信，阻断伪造 RIP 路由更新。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-13T00:00:00Z","references":["https://www.cve.org/CVERecord?id=CVE-1999-0111"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-0252.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-0188","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-0188.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-0076","title":"WU wu-ftpd PASV命令缓冲区溢出漏洞","description":"wu-ftpd 的 PASV 命令存在缓冲区溢出漏洞，远程攻击者可通过向目标 FTP 服务器发送特制的 PASV 命令请求触发该漏洞，导致 wu-ftpd 进程崩溃并产生 core dump 文件。该漏洞影响早期版本的 wu-ftpd 服务程序，攻击者无需身份认证即可触发拒绝服务，在特定环境下可能进一步实现远程代码执行。","severity":"MEDIUM","score":5.0,"aliases":["CVE-1999-0076"],"sources":["epss"],"published":"1997-07-01T04:00:00.000","updated":"2026-06-16T21:47:31.463","remediation":"立即升级 wu-ftpd 至 2.6.2 或更高版本，该版本已修复 PASV 命令缓冲区溢出漏洞。如无法升级，可在 wu-ftpd 配置文件中限制 PASV 命令的使用范围，或在防火墙层面限制对 FTP 服务（端口 21）的访问来源 IP。鉴于 wu-ftpd 已停止维护，建议迁移至 vsftpd 或 ProFTPD 等仍在活跃维护的 FTP 服务器软件。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-13T00:00:00Z","references":["https://exchange.xforce.ibmcloud.com/vulnerabilities/CVE-1999-0076"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-0188.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-0186","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-0186.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-0074","title":"Linux Kernel TCP 端口顺序分配欺骗漏洞","description":"Linux 内核 TCP 协议栈在分配监听端口时采用顺序递增方式，导致远程攻击者可通过预测后续端口号实施 TCP 会话劫持与 IP 欺骗攻击。该漏洞影响早期 Linux 内核版本，攻击者无需任何身份认证即可在未建立连接的条件下伪造 TCP 数据包，破坏通信完整性。后续内核版本改用了随机端口分配机制修复此问题。","severity":"MEDIUM","score":6.4,"aliases":["CVE-1999-0074"],"sources":["epss"],"published":"1997-07-01T04:00:00.000","updated":"2026-06-16T21:47:31.197","remediation":"升级 Linux 内核至 2.0.40 或 2.2.27 及以上版本，这些版本已实现 RFC 1948 随机化 TCP 序列号机制。如无法升级，可通过 sysctl 启用 tcp_tw_reuse 和 tcp_syncookies 提升抗欺骗能力，并在网络边界配置 ACL 限制源地址伪造。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-13T00:00:00Z","references":["https://www.cve.org/CVERecord?id=CVE-1999-0074"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-0186.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-0807","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-0807.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-0541","title":"多个厂商 WWW 服务存在可猜测密码漏洞","description":"WWW URL 访问密码可被猜测或暴力破解，攻击者通过常见弱口令字典或自动化枚举工具即可获取受保护资源的未授权访问权限，受影响的 Web 应用可能因此泄露敏感数据、遭受未授权操作或完全被攻击者控制。该漏洞影响广泛，涉及使用 HTTP 基本认证或表单认证的多种 Web 服务。","severity":"HIGH","score":7.5,"aliases":["CVE-1999-0541"],"sources":["cve","epss"],"published":"1997-07-01","updated":"2026-06-16","remediation":"使用强密码策略（大小写字母、数字、特殊字符组合，长度不少于12位），部署账户锁定机制和多因素认证，避免使用默认凭据或常见弱口令。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-16T23:58:38.634464831+00:00","references":["https://www.cve.org/CVERecord?id=CVE-1999-0541"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-0807.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-0798","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-0798.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-0532","title":"DNS 服务器区域传输未授权访问信息泄露漏洞","description":"DNS 区域传输（Zone Transfer）是 DNS 主从服务器间同步域名数据库的标准机制。当 DNS 服务器未正确限制区域传输的发起来源时，任意远程攻击者均可通过发送 AXFR 查询请求获取该域名的全部 DNS 记录，包括 A/AAAA 记录、MX 邮件交换记录、CNAME 别名记录、NS 名称服务器记录及 TXT 文本记录等。攻击者利用这些信息可绘制目标网络的完整拓扑结构，识别关键服务器 IP 地址，为后续针对性攻击（如 DDoS 放大攻击、钓鱼攻击）提供情报支撑。该漏洞通常由 DNS 服务器配置不当导致，影响 BIND、Microsoft DNS Server 等主流 DNS 服务软件。","severity":"MEDIUM","score":5.0,"aliases":["CVE-1999-0532"],"sources":["cve"],"published":"1997-07-01","updated":"2026-07-16","remediation":"限制区域传输仅允许授权的从服务器 IP 地址，在 BIND 中使用 allow-transfer 配置项或设置成 none，并启用 TSIG 签名认证机制增强传输安全性，定期审计 DNS 服务器日志监控异常 AXFR 请求。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-16T00:00:00Z","references":["https://www.cve.org/CVERecord?id=CVE-1999-0532","https://nvd.nist.gov/vuln/detail/CVE-1999-0532","https://github.com/websecnl/Bulk_CVE-1999-0532_Scanner","https://github.com/Rodney-O-C-Melby/dns-zone-transfer-test","https://github.com/SleepTheGod/dns-zone-audit"],"poc_urls":["https://github.com/websecnl/Bulk_CVE-1999-0532_Scanner","https://github.com/Rodney-O-C-Melby/dns-zone-transfer-test"],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":["https://raw.githubusercontent.com/adysec/AVE/main/pocs/1999/POC-AVE-1999-0798.toml"],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":true,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-0798.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-0340","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-0340.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-0169","title":"NFS 虚假UID认证绕过漏洞","description":"NFS（网络文件系统）协议存在认证缺陷，其基于 UID（用户 ID）的访问控制机制未对客户端身份进行有效验证。远程攻击者无需合法凭据，仅需在 NFS 请求中伪造特权用户（如 root）的 UID 值，即可绕过文件权限检查，实现对目标系统上任意文件的读取与写入操作。该漏洞影响广泛部署的 NFS 服务实现，CVSS v2 评分 10.0，危害等级严重，可导致敏感数据泄露、系统文件篡改乃至完全控制服务器。由于 NFS 协议设计阶段未内置强认证机制，此问题属于架构性安全缺陷。","severity":"MEDIUM","score":5.0,"aliases":["CVE-1999-0169"],"sources":["epss"],"published":"1997-07-01","updated":"1997-07-01","remediation":"升级 NFS 服务端至 NFSv4 版本，配置 /etc/exports 中启用 root_squash 和 all_squash 选项强制将远程用户映射为匿名用户，避免直接绕过权限检查；同时使用 sec=krb5 或 sec=krb5p 启用 Kerberos 认证，防止客户端伪造 UID/GID。在无法升级的场景下，应在防火墙层面限制 NFS 端口（2049/TCP/UDP）仅允许受信 IP 段访问，并使用 exports 的 rw/ro 和 subnet 限制作为临时缓解。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-13T00:00:00Z","references":[],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-0340.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-0325","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-0325.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-0156","title":"wu-ftpd FTP 守护进程认证绕过漏洞","description":"wu-ftpd FTP 服务程序存在认证绕过漏洞，远程攻击者无需有效凭据即可使用任意用户名和密码组合成功登录目标服务器。该漏洞源于 wu-ftpd 在用户身份验证过程中未正确校验账户凭证，导致攻击者可绕过认证机制获取服务器访问权限，进而读取、上传或删除文件。此漏洞影响所有使用 wu-ftpd 的早期 Unix/Linux 系统。","severity":"MEDIUM","score":4.6,"aliases":["CVE-1999-0156"],"sources":["cve"],"published":"1997-07-01","updated":"2026-06-16","remediation":"立即升级 wu-ftpd 至 2.5 及以上版本，或停止使用已停止维护的 wu-ftpd，迁移至 vsftpd、ProFTPD 等仍在维护的 FTP 服务端。如无法立即迁移，可在防火墙层面限制对 FTP 端口（21）的访问来源 IP，并禁用匿名登录。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-13T00:00:00Z","references":["https://www.cve.org/CVERecord?id=CVE-1999-0156","https://nvd.nist.gov/vuln/detail/CVE-1999-0156"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-0325.toml"}]